structure.name: UBX-MON-SYS
structure.description: This message contains operationally relevant system information for monitoring purposes. cpuLoadMax value is only valid, if 1 second output frequency is set. Detailed information about ioUsage/ioUsageMax are available in UBX-MON-COMMS message. tempValue has an accuracy of +/- 2 deg.
